PrecisConfirmation of a By-law Amending the HAMILTON HARBOUR COMMISSIONERS' LAND USE AND DEVELOPMENT BY-LAW which introduces and defines seven new terms, clarifies the meaning of four existing ones, improves the French terminology, describes land development procedures more precisely and clearly specifies the kind of plans that must be submitted to the Commissioners prior to development.
